The original issue happened because `sukima.me##header > div.v-toolbar__content div[class="container"]` does not match any longer. This can be fixed with
```
sukima.me#$#.gray-50[style="border-bottom:1px solid #eee;height:50px;"] { display: none !important; }
sukima.me#$#header > div.v-toolbar__content { height: 52px!important; }
```

I'll add these, but will keep the `trusted-click-element` rule in case they change site's structure again.

